###

### Add basketLine to basket
POST localhost:8080/api/basket/items
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "dishId": "f53317ab-163b-4c4b-8fd1-c75eb8c404b2",
  "restaurantId": "0c8bf7b5-7330-4d3d-b8f1-2d067b0a6ebc",
  "customerSessionId": "9eeec569-d99e-4c03-93bc-f1e152363873"
}


###

### Remove basketLine from basket
DELETE localhost:8080/api/basket/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dishId": "f53317ab-163b-4c4b-8fd1-c75eb8c404b2",
  "basketId": "efcae5bc-678b-40ae-a1c8-a9988bf35c4e"
}


